app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2073-4425/12/2/299/s1: Figure S1: Distribution of applied AC EF strength in a 6-well plate during hTCEpi cell stimulation (electric potential: 200 mV; frequency: 20 Hz; wave form). Figure S2: Analysis of the gene and protein array data: (A) principal component analysis of the RMA-normalized microarray data; (B) hierarchical clustering of the protein extracts based on differentially expressed proteins. Figure S3: Analysis of the gene array data: (A) clustering heat map of the calibrated samples; (B) volcano plot of the differentially expressed genes. Table S1: Gene array data. Table S2: Antibody array data.
